    [ 3116.052895] #PF: error_code(0x0002) - not-present page
    [ 3116.058636] PGD 100000067 P4D 100000067 PUD 1001f2067 PMD 10f82e067 PTE 0
    [ 3116.066221] Oops: 0002 [#1] SMP NOPTI
    [ 3116.092948] RIP: 0010:iowrite32+0x9/0x76
